<p>To switch off your computer:</p>

<steps>
  <item>
    <p>Click your name on the top bar</p>
  </item>
  <item>
    <p>Click <gui>Power Off</gui></p>
  </item>
</steps>

<p>You may want to power off your computer if you wish to move it and do not have a battery, if your battery low or does not hold charge well. A powered off computer also uses <link xref="power-batterylife">less energy</link> than one which is suspended.</p>

